#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.76:1.1"
msgid ""
"… “Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appakā te sattā ye pharusāya vācāya paṭiviratā; "
"atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā ye pharusāya vācāya appaṭiviratā … pe …."
msgstr ""
"“… the sentient beings who refrain from harsh speech are few, while those "
"who don’t refrain are many. …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
